Class Team

  • java.lang.Object
    • countryComponents.Team
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class Team
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Team>, java.io.Serializable
    Project #4 CS 2334, Section 010 April 16, 2015

    Holds a PersonList of team members, the name of the city in which they are based, and the name of the state that city is in.
